{"tid":1288752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉細良談七一衝擊, 預料:官員會與抗爭者一同清算, 立即普選唯一出路, 未來香港抗爭將激進化","createTime":"2019-07-05T18:25:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T06:35:08.000Z","uid":197213,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2a48eb6209b3d34ac9f3ec9971c1a712f639c671","tid":1288752,"uid":197213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:25:25.000Z","msg":"【七一衝擊】專訪劉細良談現場目擊七一衝擊由來，港警大搜捕將迫使香港全面抗共，林鄭月娥變壞的原因以及下場<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RZ_I8xENYp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRZ_I8xENYp4&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHfMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=b57d8439\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RZ_I8xENYp4</a><br />\n<br />\n訪談要點：<br />\n一，現場目擊七一衝擊前因後果。<br />\n二，制度暴力將學生逼上絕路；<br />\n三，主流民意同情學生<br />\n四，中共、港府的冷血，將迫使香港民主運動矛頭對準中共。<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得非常有參考價值, <br />\n<br />\n自己覺得有幾點幾重要,<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. (28:00)由於香港管治模式已與大陸無異:公檢法, 傳媒控制, 政府獨斷,<br />\n 一國兩制呢個假面具已經被過去一個月間既抗爭運動撕破。<br />\n<br />\n---&gt;香港人會愈黎愈唔接受換人呢個玩法, <br />\n變左只有<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">立即普選</span></span></strong>, 係解決宜家呢個局既方法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. (28:21)由於開槍既底線已經被跨過, 橡膠子彈只會愈黎愈常見, (<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:好似D催淚彈咁),<br />\n    而武力升級只會激使以死相搏既年輕人<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">更激進化</span></strong>, 係一條不歸路....<br />\n<br />\n3. (21:59)<strong> <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">香港會為全球國際既抗共前線</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n4. (03:55)七一警退, 大極機會為中方命令: 七一不能流血, 否則<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">七一將會成為中港永久傷痕</span></strong>, 所以七二凌晨才清場。港府雖非特意設局, 仍有意利用, 以作輿論反撲。<br />\n<br />\n5. (14:21) <strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">林鄭下場</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n其實仲有, 不過太眼訓, 幫推"},{"pid":"47d9e7358fe292324506475e0d865ea2ea057459","tid":1288752,"uid":197213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:25:58.000Z","msg":"冇野講"},{"pid":"d7b416916e956aa2afda481d87a1ad8058bb8079","tid":1288752,"uid":197213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:27:04.000Z","msg":"冇野講"},{"pid":"8872b13b470ff97bfa4f841ab5a4f89206314f75","tid":1288752,"uid":197213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:28:53.000Z","msg":"冇野講"},{"pid":"f53a4abef4ee580520d89abe0c299c3cf1f7642d","tid":1288752,"uid":58841,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:33:42.000Z","msg":"老實講<br />\n習敗北搞永續個刻開始<br />\n中共走向滅亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4383ad0bca293f8d21fcc48e62f71b11b86d394","tid":1288752,"uid":49329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:37:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ab45ce85c7430bc33e6b7f25b8ae7e136447bd","tid":1288752,"uid":197213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:37:46.000Z","msg":"冇野講"},{"pid":"3c3cb5a5c1e7163a9110e62c24f17cb69295d730","tid":1288752,"uid":53369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:46:00.000Z","msg":"呢條片冇用<br />\n聽城寨點打輿論戰好過"},{"pid":"87a48ef8c2d49fa31ed86fe8c8d3a5c0359e075e","tid":1288752,"uid":197213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c3cb5a5c1e7163a9110e62c24f17cb69295d730","tid":1288752,"uid":53369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:46:00.000Z","msg":"呢條片冇用<br />\n聽城寨點打輿論戰好過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:49:21.000Z","msg":"純粹係一個形勢 同未來既展望"},{"pid":"ec8771757b47894cfdc07e5735e8c1c9d05621cb","tid":1288752,"uid":207942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:53:05.000Z","msg":"冇野講"},{"pid":"f71ea0075d81d518145558c40